in","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d90e63f805","type":"subtitle","text":"诗集目录","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d599962b76","type":"paragraph","text":"挖仙米        1","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"03a4f4c641","type":"paragraph","text":"五里双饿殍    2","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"846b204845","type":"paragraph","text":"千担坵有见    2","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"06ecec2edc","type":"paragraph","text":"塔山坡有见    3","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a2e3b2c2c8","type":"paragraph","text":"四娘忧        3","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d2e9a92eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"喊魂          3","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"39558f37ac","type":"paragraph","text":"四爷死        4","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"63aefe826d","type":"paragraph","text":"岳丈死        5","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"c2f38c037c","type":"paragraph","text":"割麦          5","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"fcb7acbb61","type":"paragraph","text":"打麦          5","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"8c98fa5038","type":"paragraph","text":"车水          6","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9261439987","type":"paragraph","text":"过端午        6","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"239564b9fc","type":"paragraph","text":"喜挖野红苕    6","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"0f0e53da0f","type":"paragraph","text":"大粑粑        7","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b072e6eddb","type":"paragraph","text":"食糠          7","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"edc58ebe3a","type":"paragraph","text":"吃仙米        7","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9a97851d84","type":"paragraph","text":"佳音展翅飞    7","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"f5c2b0eef1","type":"paragraph","text":"致邓自立      8","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"99472d3b6c","type":"paragraph","text":"卖儿          9","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"24f59c6883","type":"paragraph","text":"致马凡陀     10","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"20dfd84592","type":"paragraph","text":"致郭沫若     10","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"7028896274","type":"paragraph","text":"附民谣       11","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"63bff50891","type":"paragraph","text":"[注：所标注页码为原件页码]","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a4e2578ca2","type":"subtitle","text":"挖仙米①","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"1747a38bdf","type":"paragraph","text":"徐家堰，徐春良。读书在迎祥，六月四日逢星期，结伴弟兄和乡亲。跋涉50里，隆昌挖仙米。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"590636f8c3","type":"paragraph","text":"全家人六口，每天粮二斤。新发自留地，手掌一般大。土地宁荒芜，不让个人种；每栽一窝瓜，上缴四十斤，藤叶全上秤，难保任务清。只因糠菜少，泥土塞肚饱。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"ae3db37cb8","type":"paragraph","text":"路长脚无力，竹林全歇气。阿叔趁有伴，早晨没吃饭。放下担，汗珠连。腹内咕咕叫，跪啃仙米鲜。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"dbb69755fe","type":"paragraph","text":"过路人相劝，多吃难大便。大婶气愤说，不饿谁肯干？②只等双眼闭，饿死免灾难。好心指前途，秋收好光景。众口纷纷说，早死免灾祸。猪牛死，粪当药，白水庄稼苗难活。肚子饿，懒干活。顺手指田野，草比禾苗多。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d44cb84da6","type":"paragraph","text":"①即观音土；②即吃的心思。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"ed965f7988","type":"subtitle","text":"五里双饿殍","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"24f08f0183","type":"paragraph","text":"隆昌古文庙，法院共墙道。堂皇大门外，水肿倒夜半。是来求公道？是求神贤教？","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"6fbe3ca764","type":"paragraph","text":"明知罪魁首，谁敢断公道？腐儒忧国是，右派遭恶报。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"f72c420efc","type":"paragraph","text":"邱家湾裁缝，来自古音庙。非访亲故旧，进城治饿痨。久肿脚无力，望城坡边倒。新麦才收完，征购多欠交。形势无限好，五里双饿殍。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"720e33dd65","type":"subtitle","text":"6月4日千担坵有见①","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"4159391d2e","type":"paragraph","text":"郑富贵，红旗社，远近四方都晓得②。县委作重点，宣传性优越。仅后两三年，面目不认得。小春平常年，饥饿风偷窃。葫豆多生食，收种还差额。三人一斤粮，小孩打对折。饿肠又饿肚，无力举锄头。正当夏忙时，长卧千担坵。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"6c16d46c5b","type":"paragraph","text":"十岁菜色女，禾中采园叶。掺食观音土，求饱管后忧！","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b58c9872d1","type":"paragraph","text":"怨人不怨天，众口骂青山。粮食饱龟肚③，四处有荒田。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"4dfd6c4b85","type":"paragraph","text":"①千担坵——因田长而得名；②即知道；③农民挑送征购粮时，戏称喂乌龟。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a45b490e35","type":"subtitle","text":"塔山坡有见","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"401ec0035b","type":"paragraph","text":"义务劳动欢，塔山成桑园。养蚕织蜀锦，扬名展博览。雨好泥土厚，枝密叶不透。家中不养蚕，采桑装空肚。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"492290cd21","type":"subtitle","text":"四娘忧","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"e84d67d050","type":"paragraph","text":"四爷庄稼手，邻里不绝口。久饿为衰竭，换工去喂牛。脚肿无力站，跪挥割草刀。三肿又三消①，眼看进坟包。想闻油腥味，四娘苦心焦。饿偷嫩葫豆，鸡兔全没收。种贵无钱买，家中禽毛无。土改得蚊帐，合家喜洋洋。秋夜不蚊咬，酣睡甜又香。卖帐救爷病，买得黄鳝香；老小饿两天，我爷饱一餐，苦耕不得饱，人间哪公道？","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"1e06cb00a5","type":"paragraph","text":"①指水肿反复。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"e00607a03d","type":"subtitle","text":"喊魂","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"f43bca84be","type":"paragraph","text":"阿兄死“四七”①，四爷又倒床。弟兄本亲热，莫附哥哥丧②。听信邻里劝，四娘朝暮忙。坟前声声叫，四爷魂还乡。双女望抚育，牛吼要草料。喊罢发咒语，迷信命不保。不用灵丹药，饭饱水肿消。抬头问苍天，毛主席他何时倒？","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"cf9ea337c1","type":"paragraph","text":"①农民死后，以七天附计期祭悼，“亡七”为止；","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9db8e26e78","type":"paragraph","text":"②继亲人后死，称赴前者丧。[如]病后到前者坟前呼名喊魂，据说可挽救。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"ccba52e285","type":"subtitle","text":"四爷死","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"229f7b65a7","type":"paragraph","text":"四爷夜半呼不应，天明只会喘粗气。捱到中午四肢冷，黄口大张眼不闭。大婆干哭号，四娘如木鸡。双女尸前跪，不解父死悲。老古规，烧床草，从没吃剂药，药罐何处找①？机灵出主心，羹碗来代替。无棺材，只软窖，凶年不怕人耻笑。队长议众人，多念四爷勤。社有旧车箱，送与四爷把尸装。青壮白帮忙，抬爷埋山岗。登麦仅双月，十户三夫绝。眼看成新鬼，可为二、三客。谷吊黄，饿断肠，逃过夏荒关，不死是神仙。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"36dbb20870","type":"paragraph","text":"①民俗人死烧床草，扔药罐于村边。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"f778763afb","type":"subtitle","text":"岳丈死","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9750f3cbf9","type":"paragraph","text":"四爷死，岳丈远来悼。脚肿腿无力，念甥哀女婿。四爷葬，丈人无力还家乡。女请邻人抬，只求肚饱不要钱。莫怨女儿狠，让爹成野鬼。众人齐声叹，凶年人命贱。丈赴四爷丧，后继何人当？","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"3f058aa89b","type":"subtitle","text":"割麦","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b749d8ffa7","type":"paragraph","text":"天色雨水调，白水庄稼好。新麦高又茂，捆重无力桃。割麦不到午，饥肠叫咕咕。食堂只煮羹，吃粑靠自身。四顾无生人，麦穗装在身。回家用锅煎，夜半合家欢。从前偷盗羞，三辈不喂红鸡公。如今个个盗，饥饿人不笑。村野处处骂，声声斥教条，跃进新鲜事，丰年有饿殍！","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"bfe6d2da84","type":"subtitle","text":"打麦","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"65205563a8","type":"paragraph","text":"破烂石灰坝，打麦噼噼啪。同志来服务，尽快完征购。腹空手无力，慢动笑谈稀。同志解手走，生麦塞进口。大人腰包满，小孩回家转。同志回麦场，齐声加油忙。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"e50de7b363","type":"appellation","text":"车水","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b61caf6ee8","type":"paragraph","text":"龙骨水车重，四脚难踏动。宁愿阴间做饿鬼，不愿阳间车河水。当年互助组，干饭装满肚。外加幺饷午①，灌田一亩五。朝喝两碗羹，车未动，肚已空。四人同拼命，只当半天工。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"6e6bffc832","type":"paragraph","text":"①栽秧、车水时，午饭前食粑加餐[叫幺晌午]。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"6f7c3e895b","type":"subtitle","text":"过端午","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"c20408a68f","type":"paragraph","text":"小孩屈指数端午，去年曾尝麦泥鳅①。春节半斤死牛肉，过节与常总不同。听说有照顾，二两糖，五钱肉，到头原是一场空。半斤黄豆充口粮，五钱菜油熬清汤。百万死水肿，幸存饥难度。腹空糠菜少，汨罗哪来粽②。端午诗人节，诗人命途蹇。昧心歌升平，名利双获得。缄口不唱歌，保命得苟活。术民悲惨死，立刻遭横祸。但看太史简，后继如何作？","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"214cc278fc","type":"paragraph","text":"①麦制曷，状似泥鳅；②糯米制品。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"2c81fb55b5","type":"subtitle","text":"喜挖野红苕","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"5256c5a3df","type":"paragraph","text":"除草高粮地，举锄无力气。喜把野红苕，泥食甜如蜜。若再有半节[截]，锄头会高举。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"f4bd941aee","type":"subtitle","text":"大粑粑①","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"725216ae2f","type":"paragraph","text":"炊事员，本领强，做个大粑粑，分食全食堂。只因粉太少，碗中人影倒。妇女好梳头，不用把镜找。肚子胀得痛，心中饿得慌，羹清不如稠米汤。吃饭不用筷，喝完无沉淀。用舌舔饭钵，省事又节约。羹羹倒在地，流动快如飞。纵是好猎狗，奋力地难追。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"db38364e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"①戏称羹，北方称糊糊。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"bd8218a2ff","type":"subtitle","text":"食糠","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"50444f1804","type":"paragraph","text":"久晴瓜菜少，妹饥忙磨糠。久嚼难下咽，快吞大便难。教条天良灭，久狂人死绝。鹿、马欺人世，屠民不见血。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d3a5c74ad6","type":"subtitle","text":"吃仙米","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"afd0e79a2b","type":"paragraph","text":"妹肚饿，懒上学。挖得观音土，掺食麦壳壳。泥粑不用钱，全家尽饱餐。只求肚不饿，管它后来祸①。","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a13ec64a04","type":"paragraph","text":"①食观音土后，往往因便结而死。","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"e3e334f936","type":"subtitle","text":"佳音展翅飞","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"66e15fe59e","type":"paragraph","text":"新麦完征购，赔产口粮扣。久晴瓜菜少，夏荒命难逃。队长开会归，佳音展翅飞。倍加自留地，饿眼闪星星。苦熬四十天，高粮熟半吊。割食塞肚饱，种好印度苕①。猪牛死，粪肥少。只要勤锄草，白水庄稼也会好。人有红苕吃，苕苗作猪料。公私得兼顾，水肿病会消。早学邓自立，民间灾难少。叹罢舒愁眉，忠良胜奸臣！","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"5fb78a0f60","type":"paragraph","text":"①红苕良种。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"582e9eda93","type":"subtitle","text":"致邓自立①","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"8b5a977c55","type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的地委书记，不知您做什么工作？身在何地？大家都念您，向您致谢，向您敬礼，向您报告好消息：又分得了蔬菜土、自留地。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"e90a7e7f20","type":"paragraph","text":"在天狗吃太阳的日子②，小人当道，说您倒退，说您右倾，这是奸臣陷害，皂白不分。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"6e036d7f85","type":"paragraph","text":"口粮低标准，糠菜也不饱。猪牛死，人饿倒，肥土不长苗，遍地是野草；不收自留地，瓜菜长得好。人有吃，猪有料，城乡无饿殍。听说您下放？我们心插刀。您如饿肚子，我们愿乞讨。终生来奉养，长寿永不老。如果准修庙，合力金身造。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a6bc3e43eb","type":"paragraph","text":"听说飞机来迎接③，我们欢喜了不得。从今展大志，万民全声附。自留地还原，苦熬四十天。半吊高粮熟，蚁命得苟延。大力种红苕，人猪双得饱。七年不变动，生活日渐好。公私得兼顾，国民全富裕。喂肥过年猪，酿得糯米酒，礼请书记坐上头。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9bc5f50665","type":"paragraph","text":"偷天火的菩萨，代介指纪念他。说好话做坯事的人，公道不会容情。撕破假面皮，送他上法庭。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d14a08dc27","type":"paragraph","text":"①前沪州地委书记，因分自留地，饲料地而被撤职，农民中流传着极多有关他的传说，甚至成为神话；②即日蚀；③传说毛主席用飞机接他到北京。","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d97deff2a6","type":"subtitle","text":"卖儿","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b9535df676","type":"paragraph","text":"付家公社曾吉昌，家住泡桐树。自幼织麻布，庄稼活不熟。月月吃口粮，钱从何处出？全家人七口，二斤粮不足。争食一口羹，兄妹骂双亲。多食仙米粑，儿女皮包骨。眼看要短命，爹妈割心愁。去年葬父卖幼儿，今天逃生四郎送。莫怨娘狠毒，牵儿大门出。新爹罕男子，待汝掌上珠。您娘不饿死，有饭重相逢。","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"eb0f5219e9","type":"subtitle","text":"致马凡陀","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"06b46c1be6","type":"paragraph","text":"寄语马凡陀，请为饿鬼歌。勿为名位累，后世无楷模！","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b5a05c793d","type":"subtitle","text":"致郭沫若","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"5207ba50b5","type":"paragraph","text":"女神太浪漫，","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"371b82c4aa","type":"paragraph","text":"她和凡人无关；","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"0e5626dbb9","type":"paragraph","text":"百花纵然鲜艳 ，","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"dc355987fb","type":"paragraph","text":"肚子正饿的人，","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"367f9ab20f","type":"paragraph","text":"无心肠去看。","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"7e5599a8e0","type":"paragraph","text":"水牛当歌，","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"dee20743ff","type":"paragraph","text":"因为拖拉机很少。","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"2857107624","type":"paragraph","text":"只因人不饱，","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"1c6d97f188","type":"paragraph","text":"牛栏缺青草。","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a007505171","type":"paragraph","text":"老牛难过冬，","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"74f1f95769","type":"paragraph","text":"嫩口①毛多肉很少。","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a3a1e976d1","type":"paragraph","text":"郭老！郭老！","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"18e26f059a","type":"paragraph","text":"您可知道？","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"cad6a8efa6","type":"paragraph","text":"天府故里，","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"661e444447","type":"paragraph","text":"野有饿殍；","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b82202bc66","type":"paragraph","text":"清将疾苦，","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b7f976b77c","type":"paragraph","text":"笔底波涛。","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9c61128b7d","type":"paragraph","text":"提醒栋梁，","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"98617dfe6d","type":"paragraph","text":"民命为要。","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"50e79ace85","type":"paragraph","text":"粉饰太平，","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"d0fe2b290c","type":"paragraph","text":"后人贻笑！","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"01960c3be0","type":"paragraph","text":"邦凶作恶，罪恶难逃！","index":120,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a5a4145b7e","type":"paragraph","text":"①即仔牛。","index":121,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a9799a701c","type":"paragraph","text":" 李盛照于四川隆昌乐只乡1961.07","index":122,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"1a9e9c4663","type":"subtitle","text":"民谣","index":123,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"1e8f674829","type":"subtitle","text":"—李盛照辑","index":124,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"2048605f41","type":"paragraph","text":"大干部大偷，小干部小偷，（食堂）管理负责挖腹心油，社员偷点儿毛毛秋（菜）。","index":125,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"51684e3191","type":"paragraph","text":" （隆昌光荣公社，曾祥先，贫农）","index":126,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"5f1a66edfb","type":"paragraph","text":"水肿病，要死完，土地要还原，二天（以后）吃都吃不完。","index":127,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"8b5ea1aa2b","type":"paragraph","text":" 1961年5月25日艾新容（小土地出租）。","index":128,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"efd5d96f5a","type":"paragraph","text":"刘淑一（贫农）讲：","index":129,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"e4b2282d2e","type":"paragraph","text":"肥干部，瘦社员，不肥不瘦炊事员。","index":130,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"2f32090266","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席哪天垮台？毛主席是来收生的！","index":131,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"1a3b9baf74","type":"paragraph","text":" 5月20日陈清和（中农）讲。","index":132,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a9d3617a0b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席何时倒霉？","index":133,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9e7cc530a2","type":"paragraph","text":" 林四娘（贫农）6月11日。","index":134,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"01d2720119","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席拿刀来割颈子，图个快（即速死）。","index":135,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"0118668a17","type":"paragraph","text":" （曾正富，贫农）6月13日 。","index":136,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"9f5fceac21","type":"paragraph","text":"有做无吃，哪朝哪代都没得这个道理，只怪茅山道娃儿。","index":137,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"a023772766","type":"paragraph","text":" 陈清民，小土地6月29日。","index":138,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"b1f89ed988","type":"paragraph","text":"饿死不如造死！","index":139,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"},{"id":"3d4128c372","type":"paragraph","text":" 赖贺芳，贫农。","index":140,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23"}],"page":{"id":"a78bf602e1","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a1829ceb23","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}